[
  {
    "start": 0.4,
    "end": 5.6,
    "text": "Welcome to learning English at home.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 2.8,
    "end": 7.919,
    "text": "Today we're taking off with real airport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 5.6,
    "end": 9.92,
    "text": "English conversations. From booking a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 7.919,
    "end": 11.84,
    "text": "taxi to flight delays, shopping",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 9.92,
    "end": 14.24,
    "text": "duty-free, and meeting friends at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 11.84,
    "end": 16.56,
    "text": "arrivals. These dialogues will help you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 14.24,
    "end": 19.199,
    "text": "speak English naturally and confidently",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 16.56,
    "end": 21.84,
    "text": "when you travel. Learning tip: Listen",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 19.199,
    "end": 24.08,
    "text": "carefully, repeat aloud, and focus on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 21.84,
    "end": 26.56,
    "text": "real phrases used by travelers and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 24.08,
    "end": 28.88,
    "text": "airport staff. Don't forget to follow,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 26.56,
    "end": 33.32,
    "text": "like, and share. Let's begin your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 28.88,
    "end": 33.32,
    "text": "English airport adventure together.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 34.32,
    "end": 39.12,
    "text": " Good morning. I'd like to book a taxi to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 37.12,
    "end": 42.32,
    "text": "the city center, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 39.12,
    "end": 43.84,
    "text": " Good morning, sir. Certainly. May I know",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 42.32,
    "end": 48.239,
    "text": "your destination?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 43.84,
    "end": 52.719,
    "text": " I'm going to the Sunrise Hotel downtown.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 48.239,
    "end": 55.44,
    "text": " All right. That's about 30 km from here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 52.719,
    "end": 57.6,
    "text": "Would you like a private taxi or the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 55.44,
    "end": 60.0,
    "text": "shared shuttle service?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 57.6,
    "end": 64.0,
    "text": "What's the difference in price?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 60.0,
    "end": 67.04,
    "text": " The private taxi costs $35 and goes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 64.0,
    "end": 71.36,
    "text": "directly to your hotel. The shared",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 67.04,
    "end": 73.76,
    "text": "shuttle is $15 per person, but it makes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 71.36,
    "end": 77.68,
    "text": "several stops along the way.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 73.76,
    "end": 81.84,
    "text": " Hm. How long does the shuttle take?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 77.68,
    "end": 85.52,
    "text": " Around 45 to 60 minutes, depending on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 81.84,
    "end": 86.96,
    "text": "traffic. The taxi usually takes about 25",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 85.52,
    "end": 90.72,
    "text": "minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 86.96,
    "end": 92.64,
    "text": "Okay, I'll take the taxi. Do I pay here",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 90.72,
    "end": 96.4,
    "text": "or to the driver?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 92.64,
    "end": 97.92,
    "text": " You can pay here by cash or card. Which",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 96.4,
    "end": 99.439,
    "text": "do you prefer?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 97.92,
    "end": 103.119,
    "text": " Card, please.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 99.439,
    "end": 107.04,
    "text": " Great. Please insert or tap your card",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 103.119,
    "end": 108.96,
    "text": "here. Done. Your taxi will arrive in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 107.04,
    "end": 113.2,
    "text": "about 5 minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 108.96,
    "end": 116.56,
    "text": " Perfect. Does the price include tolls?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 113.2,
    "end": 118.96,
    "text": " Yes, sir. Everything is included. Tolls,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 116.56,
    "end": 121.2,
    "text": "airport fee, and luggage.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 118.96,
    "end": 122.719,
    "text": " That's good to know. Could I get a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 121.2,
    "end": 125.6,
    "text": "receipt, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 122.719,
    "end": 128.64,
    "text": " Of course. Here's your printed receipt",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 125.6,
    "end": 131.84,
    "text": "and the driver's name, Mr. Tom.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 128.64,
    "end": 134.959,
    "text": " Thank you. Oh, and how will I find him?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 131.84,
    "end": 137.76,
    "text": " He'll meet you just outside at exit gate",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 134.959,
    "end": 138.959,
    "text": "B. He'll be holding a small sign with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 137.76,
    "end": 142.72,
    "text": "your name.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 138.959,
    "end": 145.76,
    "text": " Excellent. And one last question, how",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 142.72,
    "end": 148.8,
    "text": "late do the taxis operate? The taxi",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 145.76,
    "end": 151.12,
    "text": "service runs 24 hours, sir. You can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 148.8,
    "end": 153.599,
    "text": "always book through this counter or at",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 151.12,
    "end": 156.319,
    "text": "the help desk near gate 10.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 153.599,
    "end": 158.72,
    "text": " Wonderful. Thank you for your help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 156.319,
    "end": 159.76,
    "text": " My pleasure. Have a safe trip to your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 158.72,
    "end": 161.92,
    "text": "hotel.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 159.76,
    "end": 164.64,
    "text": " Thanks. Have a great day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 161.92,
    "end": 167.44,
    "text": " Key phrases you learned today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 164.64,
    "end": 169.92,
    "text": " Booking and price.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 167.44,
    "end": 173.84,
    "text": " I'd like to book a taxi to the city",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 169.92,
    "end": 177.92,
    "text": "center. What's the difference in price?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 173.84,
    "end": 180.319,
    "text": "The private taxi costs $35.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 177.92,
    "end": 183.599,
    "text": "Time and duration.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 180.319,
    "end": 188.72,
    "text": "How long does it take to the hotel? The",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 183.599,
    "end": 191.36,
    "text": "shuttle takes about 45 to 60 minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 188.72,
    "end": 195.28,
    "text": " Payment and details.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 191.36,
    "end": 198.959,
    "text": " Do I pay here or to the driver? The",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 195.28,
    "end": 203.44,
    "text": "price includes tolls and luggage.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 198.959,
    "end": 205.36,
    "text": "Can I have a receipt, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 203.44,
    "end": 208.8,
    "text": "Excuse me. Could you tell me what's",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 205.36,
    "end": 210.879,
    "text": "happening with flight 678 to London?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 208.8,
    "end": 212.72,
    "text": " Yes, sir. I'm very sorry for the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 210.879,
    "end": 215.519,
    "text": "inconvenience. The flight has been",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 212.72,
    "end": 218.879,
    "text": "delayed due to bad weather in London.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 215.519,
    "end": 220.959,
    "text": " Oh, I see. How long is the delay?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 218.879,
    "end": 225.519,
    "text": " At the moment, it's expected to depart",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 220.959,
    "end": 228.72,
    "text": "about 2 hours later around 9:45 p.m.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 225.519,
    "end": 231.44,
    "text": " 2 hours. That's quite a wait. Is there",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 228.72,
    "end": 233.519,
    "text": "any chance it could be delayed longer?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 231.44,
    "end": 235.44,
    "text": "We're monitoring the weather closely,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 233.519,
    "end": 237.519,
    "text": "but if there are any changes, we'll make",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 235.44,
    "end": 240.239,
    "text": "an announcement immediately.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 237.519,
    "end": 242.56,
    "text": " Okay, thank you. Is there anywhere I can",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 240.239,
    "end": 245.28,
    "text": "get something to eat while I wait?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 242.56,
    "end": 247.519,
    "text": " Yes, of course. Since the delay is more",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 245.28,
    "end": 250.319,
    "text": "than 1 hour, passengers will receive a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 247.519,
    "end": 252.4,
    "text": "food voucher. You can use it at any cafe",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 250.319,
    "end": 254.64,
    "text": "or restaurant in the terminal.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 252.4,
    "end": 255.599,
    "text": " That's good news. Where can I get the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 254.64,
    "end": 258.16,
    "text": "voucher?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 255.599,
    "end": 260.0,
    "text": " You can collect it right here. May I see",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 258.16,
    "end": 261.759,
    "text": "your boarding pass, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 260.0,
    "end": 264.32,
    "text": " Sure. Here it is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 261.759,
    "end": 266.24,
    "text": " Thank you. Here's your food voucher",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 264.32,
    "end": 268.56,
    "text": "worth $15.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 266.24,
    "end": 271.12,
    "text": " Thanks very much. Will I need to go",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 268.56,
    "end": 273.6,
    "text": "through security again when I come back?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 271.12,
    "end": 275.68,
    "text": " No, sir. You can return directly to the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 273.6,
    "end": 277.199,
    "text": "gate. Just keep your boarding pass and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 275.68,
    "end": 280.88,
    "text": "passport with you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 277.199,
    "end": 283.759,
    "text": " Great. And if the flight gets cancelled,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 280.88,
    "end": 286.0,
    "text": "what should I do? In that case, we'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 283.759,
    "end": 288.56,
    "text": "assist you with rebooking on the next",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 286.0,
    "end": 290.639,
    "text": "available flight or provide hotel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 288.56,
    "end": 292.88,
    "text": "accommodation if necessary.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 290.639,
    "end": 294.479,
    "text": " That's very helpful. I appreciate your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 292.88,
    "end": 296.8,
    "text": "clear explanation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 294.479,
    "end": 299.28,
    "text": " My pleasure, sir. I'll make sure any",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 296.8,
    "end": 300.88,
    "text": "updates are announced right away.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 299.28,
    "end": 303.04,
    "text": " Thank you again for your help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 300.88,
    "end": 305.759,
    "text": " You're very welcome. Have something to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 303.04,
    "end": 306.88,
    "text": "eat and please check back at 9:00 for",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 305.759,
    "end": 309.199,
    "text": "updates.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 306.88,
    "end": 311.759,
    "text": " We'll do. Have a nice evening.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 309.199,
    "end": 315.52,
    "text": " You too, sir.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 311.759,
    "end": 317.919,
    "text": "Key phrases you learned today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 315.52,
    "end": 319.759,
    "text": " Delay information.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 317.919,
    "end": 322.479,
    "text": " I could you tell me what's happening",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 319.759,
    "end": 324.88,
    "text": "with flight 678?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 322.479,
    "end": 326.72,
    "text": " The flight has been delayed due to bad",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 324.88,
    "end": 331.28,
    "text": "weather.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 326.72,
    "end": 334.4,
    "text": "It's expected to depart 2 hours later.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 331.28,
    "end": 338.88,
    "text": "Compensation and vouchers.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 334.4,
    "end": 341.44,
    "text": " Passengers will receive a food voucher.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 338.88,
    "end": 342.65,
    "text": "You can use it at any cafe or",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 341.44,
    "end": 343.919,
    "text": "restaurant.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 342.65,
    "end": 348.479,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 343.919,
    "end": 351.44,
    "text": "May I see your boarding pass, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 348.479,
    "end": 353.52,
    "text": " Next steps and politeness.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 351.44,
    "end": 355.919,
    "text": " What should I do if the flight gets",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 353.52,
    "end": 358.96,
    "text": "cancelled?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 355.919,
    "end": 361.28,
    "text": "We'll assist you with rebooking or hotel",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 358.96,
    "end": 365.56,
    "text": "stay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 361.28,
    "end": 365.56,
    "text": "Thank you for your clear explanation.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 365.84,
    "end": 371.199,
    "text": "Excuse me. Could you please help me? I'm",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 368.88,
    "end": 372.639,
    "text": "connecting to another flight and need",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 371.199,
    "end": 375.12,
    "text": "some information.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 372.639,
    "end": 376.72,
    "text": " Of course, sir. I'll be happy to help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 375.12,
    "end": 379.84,
    "text": "What would you like to know?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 376.72,
    "end": 382.88,
    "text": " I'm arriving from Singapore and flying",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 379.84,
    "end": 385.039,
    "text": "next to New York, but I'm not sure where",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 382.88,
    "end": 387.44,
    "text": "the transfer gate is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 385.039,
    "end": 388.72,
    "text": " No problem. May I see your boarding",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 387.44,
    "end": 390.479,
    "text": "pass, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 388.72,
    "end": 394.4,
    "text": " Sure. Here you go.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 390.479,
    "end": 399.28,
    "text": " Thank you. Hm. Your next flight to New",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 394.4,
    "end": 401.84,
    "text": "York departs from terminal 3, gate 25.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 399.28,
    "end": 403.6,
    "text": "You're currently in terminal 1, so",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 401.84,
    "end": 404.56,
    "text": "you'll need to take the airport shuttle",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 403.6,
    "end": 407.84,
    "text": "train.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 404.56,
    "end": 408.72,
    "text": " Oh, I see. How long does it take to get",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 407.84,
    "end": 410.88,
    "text": "there?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 408.72,
    "end": 413.28,
    "text": " The train ride takes about 10 minutes",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 410.88,
    "end": 415.52,
    "text": "and they run every 5 minutes. You'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 413.28,
    "end": 419.52,
    "text": "have plenty of time before boarding.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 415.52,
    "end": 422.8,
    "text": " Great. Thank you. Do you have an airport",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 419.52,
    "end": 425.039,
    "text": "map I can take with me? Yes, of course.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 422.8,
    "end": 428.4,
    "text": "Here's a printed map. It shows all",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 425.039,
    "end": 431.36,
    "text": "terminals, gates, and shuttle routes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 428.4,
    "end": 433.919,
    "text": " Perfect. By the way, I think I might",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 431.36,
    "end": 437.12,
    "text": "have left my jacket on the plane from",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 433.919,
    "end": 437.919,
    "text": "Singapore. Is there a lost and found",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 437.12,
    "end": 440.4,
    "text": "here?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 437.919,
    "end": 443.36,
    "text": " Yes, sir. The lost and found office is",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 440.4,
    "end": 445.44,
    "text": "located near gate 7 in this terminal.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 443.36,
    "end": 447.36,
    "text": "You can report the item there. They'll",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 445.44,
    "end": 451.039,
    "text": "contact the airline for you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 447.36,
    "end": 454.479,
    "text": " Excellent. One last thing. Are there any",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 451.039,
    "end": 456.08,
    "text": "lounges nearby? I'd like to rest before",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 454.479,
    "end": 458.319,
    "text": "my next flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 456.08,
    "end": 461.599,
    "text": " Absolutely. There's an international",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 458.319,
    "end": 464.24,
    "text": "lounge near gate 15. You can access it",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 461.599,
    "end": 465.36,
    "text": "with your boarding pass or pay a onetime",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 464.24,
    "end": 468.0,
    "text": "entry fee.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 465.36,
    "end": 468.8,
    "text": " Sounds perfect. Thank you for all your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 468.0,
    "end": 471.199,
    "text": "help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 468.8,
    "end": 473.36,
    "text": " My pleasure, sir. Just follow the signs",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 471.199,
    "end": 475.599,
    "text": "to the shuttle. It's clearly marked in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 473.36,
    "end": 478.319,
    "text": "blue. Have a safe journey.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 475.599,
    "end": 480.72,
    "text": " Thanks again. You've been very kind.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 478.319,
    "end": 483.52,
    "text": " You're most welcome. Enjoy your trip.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 480.72,
    "end": 485.68,
    "text": " Key phrases you learned today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 483.52,
    "end": 488.56,
    "text": " Directions and transfer.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 485.68,
    "end": 491.36,
    "text": " I'm connecting to another flight.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 488.56,
    "end": 494.4,
    "text": " May I see your boarding pass, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 491.36,
    "end": 496.16,
    "text": " Your flight departs from terminal 3,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 494.4,
    "end": 498.8,
    "text": "gate 25.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 496.16,
    "end": 501.28,
    "text": " Take the airport shuttle train.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 498.8,
    "end": 503.919,
    "text": " Information and assistance.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 501.28,
    "end": 504.8,
    "text": " Do you have an airport map I can take",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 503.919,
    "end": 508.0,
    "text": "with me?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 504.8,
    "end": 510.08,
    "text": " Is there a lost and found here? Where",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 508.0,
    "end": 512.399,
    "text": "can I find the lounge?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 510.08,
    "end": 514.24,
    "text": " Politeness and closing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 512.399,
    "end": 516.08,
    "text": " Thank you for all your help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 514.24,
    "end": 518.09,
    "text": " You've been very kind.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 516.08,
    "end": 520.32,
    "text": " Have a safe journey.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 518.09,
    "end": 522.64,
    "text": "",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 520.32,
    "end": 525.76,
    "text": " Good afternoon, sir. Would you like to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 522.64,
    "end": 527.839,
    "text": "try our new perfume collection? It's on",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 525.76,
    "end": 531.519,
    "text": "promotion today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 527.839,
    "end": 533.36,
    "text": " Hello. Yes, please. It smells nice. How",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 531.519,
    "end": 536.399,
    "text": "much is this one?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 533.36,
    "end": 539.12,
    "text": " That perfume is $68.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 536.399,
    "end": 540.24,
    "text": "And if you buy two, you'll get a 10%",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 539.12,
    "end": 543.76,
    "text": "discount.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 540.24,
    "end": 546.0,
    "text": " Oh, that's a good deal. Are these prices",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 543.76,
    "end": 549.76,
    "text": "already duty-free?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 546.0,
    "end": 552.88,
    "text": " Yes, sir. All prices here are duty-free,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 549.76,
    "end": 555.6,
    "text": "meaning there's no tax. You just need to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 552.88,
    "end": 558.64,
    "text": "show your boarding pass when you pay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 555.6,
    "end": 562.24,
    "text": " Great. I'll take one bottle of this",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 558.64,
    "end": 564.08,
    "text": "perfume and maybe some chocolates, too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 562.24,
    "end": 568.0,
    "text": "How much are these?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 564.08,
    "end": 570.959,
    "text": "The large box of chocolates is $25 and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 568.0,
    "end": 573.68,
    "text": "the smaller one is $12.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 570.959,
    "end": 575.279,
    "text": " I'll take the large one, please. Can I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 573.68,
    "end": 578.399,
    "text": "pay by card?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 575.279,
    "end": 581.12,
    "text": " Of course, sir. We accept credit cards,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 578.399,
    "end": 582.48,
    "text": "debit cards, and mobile payments like",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 581.12,
    "end": 585.12,
    "text": "Apple Pay.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 582.48,
    "end": 587.92,
    "text": " Perfect. Here's my card.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 585.12,
    "end": 588.959,
    "text": " Thank you. May I also see your boarding",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 587.92,
    "end": 590.959,
    "text": "pass?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 588.959,
    "end": 595.839,
    "text": " Sure. Here it is.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 590.959,
    "end": 599.12,
    "text": " Thank you. That will be $93 in total.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 595.839,
    "end": 600.08,
    "text": " Okay, done. Could I have a receipt,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 599.12,
    "end": 602.959,
    "text": "please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 600.08,
    "end": 605.519,
    "text": " Certainly. Here's your receipt and your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 602.959,
    "end": 606.88,
    "text": "purchase. Would you like a duty-free",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 605.519,
    "end": 610.0,
    "text": "shopping bag?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 606.88,
    "end": 614.16,
    "text": " Yes, please. By the way, can I take",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 610.0,
    "end": 618.079,
    "text": "these items in my carry-on bag? Yes, but",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 614.16,
    "end": 622.0,
    "text": "remember liquids like perfumes must be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 618.079,
    "end": 624.48,
    "text": "under 100 ml and packed in a clear",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 622.0,
    "end": 628.0,
    "text": "plastic bag for security.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 624.48,
    "end": 628.88,
    "text": " Got it. And what if I have a connecting",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 628.0,
    "end": 631.44,
    "text": "flight?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 628.88,
    "end": 634.24,
    "text": " Then please keep your duty-free receipt",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 631.44,
    "end": 635.36,
    "text": "handy. Security at the next airport may",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 634.24,
    "end": 637.6,
    "text": "check it.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 635.36,
    "end": 639.04,
    "text": " Thank you for the reminder. You've been",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 637.6,
    "end": 641.92,
    "text": "very helpful.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 639.04,
    "end": 643.92,
    "text": " My pleasure, sir. Have a pleasant flight",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 641.92,
    "end": 646.16,
    "text": "and enjoy your shopping.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 643.92,
    "end": 649.04,
    "text": " Thanks. Have a great day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 646.16,
    "end": 651.519,
    "text": " Key phrases you learned today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 649.04,
    "end": 654.56,
    "text": " Buying and asking.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 651.519,
    "end": 656.64,
    "text": " How much is this perfume? Are these",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 654.56,
    "end": 659.04,
    "text": "prices duty-free?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 656.64,
    "end": 661.44,
    "text": "Can I pay by card?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 659.04,
    "end": 664.24,
    "text": " Payment and packing.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 661.44,
    "end": 666.8,
    "text": " May I see your boarding pass, please?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 664.24,
    "end": 670.16,
    "text": "Could I have a receipt?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 666.8,
    "end": 672.959,
    "text": "Would you like a duty-free shopping bag?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 670.16,
    "end": 677.36,
    "text": "Rules and travel tips.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 672.959,
    "end": 679.2,
    "text": " Liquids must be under 100 ml. Keep your",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 677.36,
    "end": 682.2,
    "text": "duty-free receipt for connecting",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 679.2,
    "end": 682.2,
    "text": "flights.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 682.8,
    "end": 687.68,
    "text": " Excuse me. Could you help me, please? I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 685.6,
    "end": 688.56,
    "text": "just arrived, but I can't find my",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 687.68,
    "end": 691.36,
    "text": "friend.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 688.56,
    "end": 692.32,
    "text": " Of course, sir. Don't worry. Who are you",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 691.36,
    "end": 695.279,
    "text": "meeting?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 692.32,
    "end": 697.76,
    "text": " My friend, Mr. Alex. He said he'd be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 695.279,
    "end": 700.8,
    "text": "waiting for me at the arrivals area.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 697.76,
    "end": 705.2,
    "text": " All right. Which flight did you come on?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 700.8,
    "end": 708.079,
    "text": " The flight from Singapore, SQ472.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 705.2,
    "end": 711.44,
    "text": "It landed about 15 minutes ago.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 708.079,
    "end": 713.68,
    "text": " Okay, that's gate 3. The meeting point",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 711.44,
    "end": 716.0,
    "text": "is just outside the gate near the coffee",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 713.68,
    "end": 718.079,
    "text": "shop. Have you checked there yet?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 716.0,
    "end": 719.6,
    "text": " Not yet. I came straight to the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 718.079,
    "end": 722.56,
    "text": "information desk.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 719.6,
    "end": 725.2,
    "text": " No problem. You can also call or message",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 722.56,
    "end": 726.72,
    "text": "your friend. There's free Wi-Fi here.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 725.2,
    "end": 729.44,
    "text": "Would you like me to show you how to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 726.72,
    "end": 730.24,
    "text": "connect? Oh, yes, please. I'm not sure",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 729.44,
    "end": 733.279,
    "text": "how.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 730.24,
    "end": 737.04,
    "text": " Sure. Just go to your phone settings and",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 733.279,
    "end": 739.6,
    "text": "select airport free Wi-Fi. Then open",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 737.04,
    "end": 742.079,
    "text": "your browser and tap connect.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 739.6,
    "end": 744.72,
    "text": " Got it. Thank you.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 742.079,
    "end": 747.44,
    "text": "Oh, he just texted me. He's stuck in",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 744.72,
    "end": 749.839,
    "text": "traffic and will arrive in 10 minutes.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 747.44,
    "end": 752.399,
    "text": " Perfect. You can wait in the arrival",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 749.839,
    "end": 754.399,
    "text": "seating area just over there near the",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 752.399,
    "end": 756.72,
    "text": "big welcome sign.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 754.399,
    "end": 759.04,
    "text": " Great. Thanks for your help. Is there a",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 756.72,
    "end": 760.079,
    "text": "place to get some water or coffee while",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 759.04,
    "end": 762.959,
    "text": "I wait?",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 760.079,
    "end": 765.839,
    "text": " Yes, there's a small cafe right next to",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 762.959,
    "end": 768.48,
    "text": "the seating area. They serve coffee,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 765.839,
    "end": 770.639,
    "text": "snacks, and bottled water.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 768.48,
    "end": 771.36,
    "text": " Excellent. I'll grab something while I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 770.639,
    "end": 774.0,
    "text": "wait.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 771.36,
    "end": 776.32,
    "text": " Sounds good. When your friend arrives,",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 774.0,
    "end": 778.8,
    "text": "he can park at the short-term parking",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 776.32,
    "end": 781.2,
    "text": "zone near exit B.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 778.8,
    "end": 782.639,
    "text": " That's perfect. You've been very kind.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 781.2,
    "end": 785.12,
    "text": "Thank you so much.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 782.639,
    "end": 787.519,
    "text": " My pleasure, sir. Enjoy your time with",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 785.12,
    "end": 789.6,
    "text": "your friend and welcome again.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 787.519,
    "end": 791.279,
    "text": " Thank you. Have a lovely day.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 789.6,
    "end": 793.68,
    "text": " You too.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 791.279,
    "end": 795.76,
    "text": " Key phrases you learned today.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 793.68,
    "end": 798.8,
    "text": " Asking for help.",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 795.76,
    "end": 801.839,
    "text": " Excuse me. Could you help me, please? I",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 798.8,
    "end": 804.639,
    "text": "can't find my friend. He said he'd be",
    "textdich": ""
  },
  {
    "start": 801.839,
    "end": 807.519,
    "text": "waiting at the arrivals area.",
    "textdich": ""
